description:
Billy Bang was one of the greatest musicians who I ever met. This interview is one of about 50, which I have done in the last 5 years. And it is very special. 
Billy Bang passed away on 11th of April 2011.
(janic)
title: BILLY BANG INTERVIEW - Muzyka z Mózgu Festival 2007
